        Impressum
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Angaben gemäß § 5 TMG</h2>

        <address class="not-italic mb-6 text-text-muted">
          <strong class="text-text">Montessori-Kinderhaus Potsdam e.V.</strong><br />
          Knobelsdorffstr. 7<br />
          14471 Potsdam<br /><br />
          Telefon: 0331 – 620 44 30<br />
          Fax: 0331 – 620 44 31<br />
          E-Mail: info@mkiha.de
        </address>

        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Bankverbindung</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
